Dialogs.Dialog: Rinko
...Boo！
Whoa！？ ...What's wrong, ▲小早川＊▲？
Don't "whoa" me. If you don't get surprised a little more, there's no excitement, is there？
Have you been hiding all this time, by any chance？
I couldn't wait for you to find me, so I came out. Hehe.
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
You look a little different today, ▲主人公＊▲.
You think so？ We're the same, right？
Hmmm... then I guess it's Rinko's fault.
What do you mean？
I have a feeling that something unusual is about to happen. Maybe that's why the people around me seem so special.
(You're pretty late, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Rinko
Sorry to keep you waiting♪
Yo. You're very excited for being late.
I was really pumped up and ready to go, but I'm late. You'll have to forgive me for that.
Yes, yes.
Hehe, that's good.
(You're not here yet, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Rinko
Hey, you were looking at all the women earlier.
Really？ So you can just stare at Rinko all the time？
Okay, then...
Wait, why are you taking me so seriously... Don't stare at me！
(Which one...)
Did you wait for me ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Rinko just arrived. It's nice sometimes to wait for your boyfriend.
Is that why？
Well, I think about a lot of things. Like... what shall we talk about today.
Well, I'll take my time next time, then.
I'm just saying it's an occasional thing. And don't be late on purpose.
I know that.
Yo, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Hehe. Date, date♪
Aren't you excited today？
It looks like my boyfriend did his best to prepare for the date. Maybe that's why.
You're putting pressure on me.
I'm counting on you！ Please.
Rinko
Oh, there you are... geez, I was looking for you.
Sorry. There were so many people, and I couldn't find you either, ▲小早川＊▲.
...then find me right away.
▲小早川＊▲？
It's nothing. Come on, let's go.
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Geez, you're too late！
Eh？ ...But I'm not late... am I？
I know, but... The couple that was just there, you know, they've been making out all the time on the side...
That made you want to do it yourself...
Huh？ That's not true！ I was in trouble because they were making a show of it. You idiot！
Rinko
You, are, late！
Sorry, my bad, ▲小早川＊▲.
Sorry does not cover it. You were late, and I got called on.
What！？ Were they hitting on you？
Well, maybe. He wasn't persistent, so it's okay, but if you're that upset, don't be late in the first place.
Yes, I understand.
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
...what's wrong？
You might be surprisingly conspicuous, even if you are far away, it's easy to recognize you.
Heh, that means it's a good thing, right？
Eh？ Um... then, I'll just say it means it's bad.
Rinko
How about a cup of tea for now？
Yeah.
Rinko
Hey, I'm feeling a bit thirsty.
Well, let's have tea.
Rinko
Hey. Let's have some tea. Sounds good.
Yeah, okay.
How about here？
Rinko
By the way, do you remember the last Valentine's Day？
The previous... you mean ours？
Yes. See, I gave you some chocolate.
Well, I remember that...
Rinko
Hehe.
Hmm？
Oh, sorry. Remembering makes me laugh. It's about White Day.
White Day, huh...
Yes. You gave a return gift to me.
Rinko
I remember Christmas...
Huh？
The Christmas I spent with you.
Oh, I see. Me too...
It's hard to forget, isn't it？
Rinko
Rinko's birthday...
What！？ ...Not today, I know.
Hmm？ Oh, that's obvious. I didn't mean that. I was just remembering.
So that was it. That's confusing.
Because I think about it sometimes... that you celebrated with me.
Yeah...
Rinko
I know this is sudden, but on your birthday, if there is anything you want, just let me know.
And you've already thought about it？
...not really.
Hmm. Well, okay.
Just, I want you to be happier than before, so I'm doing research. Do you remember what happened last time.
I remember, of course.
Rinko
Remember our last anniversary？
Anniversary is when... we started dating, right？
Yes, we celebrated it together, didn't we？
Yeah, of course I remember.
Hehe, right.
I told you I was annoyed by my lack of resources
You said it was wrong to mislead my girlfriend
You said you believed in me from the beginning, ▲小早川＊▲
You told me that you wouldn't be disappointed if I chose it
You said you'd take it because you had to
You said you were looking forward to seeing what I would give you
You said you would like Christmas more
You said you couldn't say anything at the critical moment
I thought you said you were going to be a little more honest
You asked if we could celebrate again next year
You said you hoped my next birthday would be fun too
You said you were sad to say goodbye because of all the fun
You said you didn't want to leave
You said you have a hard time having a lonely boyfriend
Instead of celebrating, you asked me to do you a favor
You said we'd see each other tomorrow and beyond
You said you didn't just need a gift, you needed words
You said we're lovers, so there's nothing to be shy about
Rinko
Of course. Rinko's BF is always thinking about Rinko, right？
I'm a little embarrassed when you say that much, though.
Rinko
Hmmm, I see. I guess that means Rinko's love is still not enough.
...Huh？
I have no other choice. I'll inject more power of love today.
(I'm glad you're not mad at me for being wrong.)
Rinko
You know... I want to stay with you like this forever. What would you do if I say that？
Eh... want to be with you, though.
...yeah, I know you're thinking the same thing. But I know it's an impossible request. Sorry, I'm being selfish.
You can be selfish with me.
Rinko
We've been to many places on dates.
Right. Where do you want to go this time？
I'm fine right here.
Here？
Yes, next to you. As long as Rinko can stay here, that's all that matters.
Rinko
I wish time would stop only around you and Rinko.
We can still be together today, right？
But it will be over soon. I wish Rinko could stay forever.
After today is over, you can go on another date with me. I'll go out with you as many times as you want.
Rinko
...aren't Rinko's hands weird？
What's wrong？
They want to hold your hand more, and they don't want to leave you.
Then that's fine. It looks like my hands are the same. Here.
Rinko
You know, Rinko sometimes envy cats.
Because they can live at will？
No, it's not. They can be pampered forever by the people they love, right？
Then you don't have to be a cat to be pampered, right？
Rinko
Isn't Rinko always the only one who spoils you？
Really？ I'd be more than happy to spoil you.
No, I don't mean that... I think I want to be pampered once in a while.
By me？ Yes, that might be a good idea...
Rinko
You know, sometimes I get really anxious when I say goodbye after a date. Is that weird？
Do I make you anxious？
No, it's not that. It's not that, but... can I hold your hand？
Yeah, okay. Until you're not anxious.
What's the matter？ You've been quiet since a while ago, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
I wanted to stare at your profile. I guess.
Mine？ Well, then, maybe I will get even with you.
I can' t look at your profile then, can I？ Come on, face forward.
Ehh.
Rinko
A date for a special occasion is still nice.
Was it a special occasion？
Yeah. A special date is a special date. Today's date is a little different.
I see... I'm glad you feel that way.
Rinko
...I think I might have some kind of fever.
What, you have a cold！？
Maybe not... I'm having fun today and I'm so excited... I'm sure that's why.
Haha. Then it's okay, me too.
Rinko
We can still be together quite a bit after this.
Yeah. I wanted to take our time on the date.
It's good to do this once in a while. Being like this.
Dating without worrying about time is great, isn't it？
Rinko
I guess I'm taking a break.
Today's just the beginning, you know？
I know. I won't leave on the way. Hehe.
Haha, don't scare me.
Rinko
We can still be together today, right？
We have plenty of time.
Hehe, yay！
Haha, you're so excited.
Rinko
There's still plenty of time, right？
We've got a lot to do today！
Yes, yes, don't get hurt in the rush.
I'm not a child...
Rinko
What are we going to do after this？
Maybe we can take it a little slower. We have time.
Hmmm, I'll leave it to you then. Escort me.
Roger that.
Rinko
Not having to worry about time is great.
Yeah, I'm still good for today.
I wish it was always like this...
Hmm？
Rinko
Hey, why don't we take a break？
Are you tired？
Just a little bit.
Then let's do that.
Rinko
How long are we going to walk？
Sorry, you must be tired.
Yeah. You don't have to be told to notice.
Right. Then let's take some rest.
Rinko
Hey. Aren't you tired？
Not much... Oh, I'm sorry. We keep walking, and I know you're tired.
A little bit.
Okay, let's rest then.
Rinko
You know what, why don't we take a break？
Yes, let's take a break here.
Yeah. Walking around is one of the best parts of a date.
Rinko
Do you know how tired your girlfriend is？
Oh, I see.
I feel like I'm here for walking.
Then we can take a little rest somewhere.
Rinko
You know what, why don't we take a break？
Are you tired, perhaps？
Just a little bit. I thought you might want to slow down.
I guess so. Let's take a break.
Rinko
You know, we've been dating a lot lately, right？
Come to think of it, that may be true.
Right？ When I think back on it, it happens all the time.
That much？
Yeah. Don't you think we've had enough dates yet？
If you don't think it's too much, then it's not enough？ Haha.
You're seriously ill. And so is Rinko who goes along with you. Hehe.
Rinko
Maybe we don't have many dates these days.
Really？ ...might be right. We need to make more time to go out together.
I'm glad to hear that too, but you don't have to.
Huh？
I'd love to date, but numbers aren't everything.
Well, that's right.
I have fun dates like today, and that's enough for me.
Rinko
Haven't I been getting a lot of calls from you lately？
Maybe it's a nuisance or something.
Of course not. I didn't mean it that way.
I just wondered if you wanted to be with Rinko all the time that much.
That may be true.
Hehe, you're so honest. You're so sweet to Rinko.
When you put it that way... well, you're not wrong.
Rinko
You haven't been calling Rinko much lately, have you？
Eh... maybe you're mad at me？
...Hehe, surprised？
I'm surprised, of course.
I don't think Rinko would be mad at you for this.
Really？
That's right. You even go on dates with me like this. I'm pretty satisfied.
Rinko
What's with all the skinship lately？
...I wonder, don't you like it？
No, it's not that. Rinko feels relieved when she is patted or gently touched by you.
I see. Good.
That's why.
Hmm？
If you don't mind, I'm fine with it as it is.
(She' s kind of honest... that's cute.)
Rinko
...Can I have a word？
What's the matter, you're all red-faced.
You know, maybe you've been holding back lately？
What do you mean？
Don't make me say it. You know, skinship and all that.
...Oh, I see. I didn't want to be too pushy.
...I'm sure that's just your kindness, though. You don't have to worry so much.
Rinko
...Hehe.
You're grinning, what's wrong with you？
I'm not grinning.
Really？
Do you wanna hear me say more？ Then I won't kiss you anymore.
Eh, no way...
We've been doing a lot of that lately, you know？ Just kidding.
Rinko
Maybe you think that's kindness？
What are you talking about？
If Rinko is this close to you, wouldn't you want to kiss... her？
I see... Maybe I haven't been doing that much lately.
Even Rinko sometimes... Ah, geez, why do you make your girlfriend say those things？
...sorry.
I'm glad you're taking care of Rinko, but...
Rinko
You know, I wonder if Rinko is really good at cooking...
I guess. Why not？
You always say it's delicious, and I'm glad to hear that. I'm not that confident.
It's okay. You can be confident that it tastes good！
...Hehe, what are you talking about？
Rinko
Rinko's not a good cook after all.
That was sudden.
Because I feel like I get screwed up a lot.
It's not about failing... it's more of a matter of taste... Sorry, am I burdening you？
No, you're not. On the contrary, I'm kind of glad.
On the contrary？
Yes, it's nice to hear you say it so clearly.
Rinko
You know, you're a voyeur, aren't you？
What！？
Oh, I made a mistake. You like taking photos, don't you？
Hehe, Rinko's not against it. I'm rather happy about that.
Rinko
You don't take many photos, do you？ Even though you have a camera.
Well, you think？ You want me to take more photos or something？
I didn't say that. I just thought you were being cautious.
That's not the case...
If that's the case, that's fine. Sometimes you are modest like that, you know？
Rinko
Do you like Rinko's fashion？
Why？
It's because you compliment me every time we go out on a date.
That's not true. It's just you always look good, ▲小早川＊▲.
I see... That's fine.
You don't have worry about that.
Because, you know, I want my boyfriend to like me.
Rinko
Is Rinko's fashion getting better？
Eh, what's wrong？
I get a lot of opinions, you know.
Sorry, I know it's tough.
Well, yes, but I don't mind. It's worth the effort if you say so.
I'm kind of happy to hear that.
Really？ Then I'm glad.
Rinko
You e-mail me a lot, don't you？
A little too much？
Nah. I'm happy. That proves that you like Rinko, doesn't it？
Well... I'm embarrassed when you say so.
Hehe.
I see. That might be a little bit of pressure.
Just go with your usual tone. That's how you are, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Hey. You don't e-mail me much these days, do you？
Sorry.... I'm not doing it on purpose.
Don't worry. I'm not blaming you.
Is that so？
I'm happy if I get a lot of e-mails, Rinko is not a child, okay？
I don't think it's a good thing if there are a lot of them.
Right？ You should be able to put your heart into each message.
Rinko
Rinko feels quite lucky. Thanks to you.
You're exaggerating. I don't know if I'm doing all that much.
In many ways... even in the smallest things. Like, when we eat together, you know what Rinko likes.
Well, I want you to have fun eating.
Hehe, you said it so casually. You're not pushing it, are you？
I'm not pushing myself.
I see... I'm glad you have a kind boyfriend.
Rinko
You're such a thing sometimes these days.
Huh？
What can I say... an animal？ A beast？
What's with that...
Well, it's more like you're forcing skinship...
Ah... sorry...
In moderation. So far, Rinko doesn't mind quite as much.
Rinko
I guess that's one of the reasons I love you...
Hmm？ You mean why you like me？
It's obvious！ Don't say it again, you idiot.
Rinko
That... That part is no good, too.
No good？ Um...
Not at all. That's why I love you so, so much.
Eh... then, what do you mean...
You idiot, don't ask any questions.
Rinko
Hey.
What？
I love you.
What？
That's one of the things I still like about you... hehe.
Rinko
I still think I love it all together.
You'll always be there for me... keep being like that.
Rinko
After all, no matter how you look at it, it's your fault.
Me？ What？
That's how you seduce Rinko...
Seduction！？
Ah... didn't mean anything weird！ ...I mean, you're letting me do what I want.
Rinko
Hey... are you crazy about Rinko？
What, that was sudden.
Answer me. I was just wondering if you are as crazy about Rinko as Rinko is about you.
That's... well...
It's not clear... Well, it's obvious if you're blushing that much.
Rinko
Can't be, no matter what I think... I love you.
Me too...
No, Rinko loves you more.
Is that so？
That's right. So don't hate me.
Rinko
That's why I love you.
What！？
I love you！ If you let me say this much, you'll be satisfied...
Rinko
Rinko might feel a little weird.
What's the matter, are you not feeling well？
Not that！ If we are talking like this, you know...
Hmm？
I think I might love you more.
Rinko
Hey, I don't know if it's okay, I'm having so much fun and being so happy. I was really happy today. I appreciate it, okay？
Rinko
...I don't know what to say, I had so much fun on today's date. I think I might have fallen in love with you again.
Rinko
Today's date... made me love you even more. It really did, you know？ I really think so.
Rinko
Today's date was... something amazing, maybe it's like an unforgettable memory...
Rinko
...Are you still grinning？ That's normal when you've had so much fun on a date. I'm quite impressed.
Rinko
I don't think I'll ever forget today. I think it was such a special date. Thanks.
Rinko
You worked a lot harder than usual. I know that, so thank you very much.
Rinko
Today is a special day, right？ Then I wanted to do something a little more special with you. Didn't you think so？
Rinko
Thanks. Today was a special date. These are the kind of memories you want to cherish.
Hmm？ Something wrong？
Rinko
I'm not saying goodbye forever, but I don't want to leave. I wonder what's wrong with Rinko...
Because if I could stay with you forever, I would...
Um, so, just a little bit longer...
What's up
Rinko
Ah... yeah... come over here.
Hmm！？
Hehe, surprised？ A parting gift... Bye.
Rinko
...is that it？ Yeah, it was fun. See you later.
Rinko
Thank you... I can't help but go home. See you later.
Rinko
A little more... Nah, I'm being selfish. Bye-bye.
Rinko
...Yes, we're done. Bye.
Rinko
Just a little more until the end... we can't help it. See you later.
Rinko
I'll see you later. Sorry for being selfish at the end.
Rinko
It's getting dark soon. Is it time to turn on the lights？
Seems like it... By the way, are you cold？
Just a little bit. But that's okay... achoo... Hehe.
Come on. Even though it's spring, it's still cold at night, so don't be too hard on yourself.
...yeah. Then I'll ask for your help.
Ask for help？
Yeah. Like this...
Wow！？
Don't run away. It's better this way.
...a little embarrassing, though.
That's fine. All the other couples are doing the same thing.
I see... Okay. We better get there soon, or they'll take the best place to see the cherry blossoms.
Yup, let's go.
Rinko
Good for you. The best place to see the show is open.
It wasn't that it was empty, but I was desperate to secure it.
Hehe, thanks▼
...It looks completely different in this way from the daytime, doesn't it？
You're right. It's kind of fantastic.
I don't want to say one cliche word like that... but I can't find a good word for it, I'm afraid.
It's beautiful, but you know...
Hmm？ What's wrong？
The time when they can bloom beautifully is a very short period of time. Just when you think they have bloomed, they quickly fall off.
Yes... But I'm sure we'll have beautiful flowers again next year.
Next year, huh... Can I come again with you...？
I guess I got a little nervous... because we talked about the cherry blossoms falling.
You don't have to worry about that.
Yeah, I know. I really do.
Just a little... hug me.
Yeah.
...I feel safer when you do this.
Let's go see the cherry blossoms next year.
Only next year...？
Not just next year, but for years to come.
Yeah, next year and the year after and beyond... I promise.
Rinko
The trees around the shrine are completely colored... Oh, ginkgo nuts are falling.
Did you pick up gingko nuts when you were little？
I did. But the smell was...
Yes. Your hands even smelled bad.
Well, that was one of those autumnal moments, wasn't it？
You smell that odor？
You, are, wrong！ That's the act of picking up gingko nuts.
Haha, I see.
When I was a little girl, I used to pick up ginkgo nuts like crazy. When I realized it, the sun was setting between the trees.
Sunset, huh... it must be beautiful.
Even then, Rinko watched the city turn red through the trees like this... until it was pitch black.
You never forget childhood memories, no matter how long they last. It's like it's burned into your mind.
I know, right？ No matter how much the city has changed, this sunset has not changed at all. It is the same sunset that Rinko remembers.
Rinko
Wow... I love the lit up autumn leaves. They are so vivid...
When Rinko was little, it was pitch black when the sun went down.
Were you afraid？
Not really... yeah, I can't lie to you, can I？
I was so scared. I felt like Rinko was the only one left behind in the world.
I remember my dad's hands were big and warm and... reassuring when he came to pick me up.
...it's cold.
The wind is picking up, so let's have something warm to drink. They're giving out amazake over there.
Yeah, let's go... here, your hand.
Ah, sure.
Hehe.
Then, I may not be able to replace your father.
But I don't mind.
The hand my dad used to pick me up when I was a little girl. Now you pick me up... Hehe.
Your hand is getting cold, ▲小早川＊▲.
This way, I can feel your temperature... It's warm.
Rinko
Hey. Can I talk to you for a second？
Hmm？
Today, there are a lot of couples, don't you think？
Yes. I read in a magazine that it was a recommended movie for lovers... Don't you like it？
Why？
I was thinking if you don't like that kind of movie, ▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko just doesn't like targeted love scenes that are not inevitable in the story.
I don't really care what genre, as long as the content is interesting.
I see, I hope today's one is interesting.
Yeah. I plan to enjoy it without undue expectations.
Rinko
...hey. Can you hold my hand...？
...Yes. Here you go.
(Are you crying, ▲小早川＊▲？)
Are you okay？ Here's my handkerchief, ▲小早川＊▲...
...thanks. This movie was good.
Yeah. But I didn't think you would be so impressed, ▲小早川＊▲.
The first half, I was thinking it was a common story.
And yet, the scene just before the climax. The hero would break up with the heroine to keep her out of danger, right？
That's one of the best places to show off.
Even though it's the love of his life that finally got through to his heart... And yet he just... says goodbye. That's too sad.
Rinko doesn't want to imagine losing the place he finally found. If that's the case, I'd rather jump into danger with him.
(I didn't know you were that emotionally involved, ▲小早川＊▲.)
Don't worry, I won't go anywhere without you, ▲小早川＊▲.
...you mean it？
I mean it. Do you think I would let you feel lonely, ▲小早川＊▲？
Promise me, okay？ Never do anything dangerous by yourself, okay？
You don't have to be that careful.
...Good. Hehe, I should be happy, but I'm kind of crying.
Rinko
Hah... I'm getting nervous. We're almost at the start of the tournament, right？
Couples tournaments, yeah. Come on, relax your shoulders.
...you forgot to change your shoes, too？
Ah, it can't be.
Honestly... we're one and the same.
I came here with a lot of energy, but I still get nervous when it comes down to it.
I don't want you to be so nervous. I expect my boyfriend to cover all of Rinko's mistakes.
Eh？ I will cover you...？
Hehe, of course, right？
...I'll do my best.
Announcement
The first round of the tournament will now begin.
Well, let's go for the first pitch, shall we？ Here we go.
Such a heavy ball is impossible for you. It'd be better to choose a lighter one, ▲小早川＊▲.
It'll be fi... oops... here goes！
(With a form like that...)
Yay！ Strike！
Eh！？ ...no way.
Sorry... If only I had gotten a spare at the end, we could have made it to the final.
Rinko
Not at all. It was pretty cool.
Are you sure？
In a manner of speaking. You covered Rinko's mistakes with a spare many times.
Of all the performers, I have the best spare rate.
We went through quite a bit of trouble. You left all the hard-to-get places, ▲小早川＊▲.
I gave my boyfriend the opportunity to play an active role.
...on purpose？
Hehe.
...that can't be.
Well, yeah. But Rinko was happier to receive the Best Partner Award than to win.
What is the prize for the Best Partner Award？
A commemorative photo of us two.
Hmm...
It's fine. I'm more than happy about the prize. I'm happy that they said we were the best partner out of so many.
You should be happy too, or else Rinko will look like an idiot.
I'm sorry, but it's not that I'm not happy.
Hehe, please continue to be Rinko's best partner for a long time to come.
You've been doing nothing but window shopping since a while ago, is there anything you want ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Perhaps my kind boyfriend is buying me something？
That's well... maybe.
Just kidding. Rinko is not going to beg you willy- nilly. I'll buy what I want by myself.
That might be lonely. I'd like to give you a gift once in a while.
I'm happy to hear that, too. But a gift's something that is filled with special feelings.
So Rinko doesn't think it's something to begrudge you unnecessarily.
That's a tough one.
It's not difficult. I just don't want a present that's just a material thing with no thought behind it.
Besides, we are high school students. I can imagine what's in your wallet.
...that too. Well, I guess I'll just enjoy window shopping like this for the rest of the evening.
Until the night, huh... Um, what's going on？
You forget？ Then, it's a secret.
Eh, you're going to hide things from your girlfriend？
It's better to have it as a surprise. We're almost there, so just sit tight and wait.
Rinko
Hey. Are we there yet？ It's all dark already.
Maybe it's time...
What！？
Amazing... is this new illumination！？ I thought illuminations were a winter thing.
At night, they light up this star illumination.
